## PLATFORM-SPECIFIC NOTES

### Nostr (Maxi - Automated)
- **Frequency:** 2x daily (morning 9-11 AM, evening 8 PM)
- **Tone:** Convergence-focused, technical, proof-of-work mindset
- **NO promotional content** - pure thought leadership and behind-scenes
- **Engagement:** Zap quality replies (100-500 sats) when warranted

### Maxi X (@Maxibtc2009)
- **Frequency:** 2-3 posts/day
- **Mix:** 35% thought leadership, 25% market commentary, 20% promotional, 20% engagement
- **Promotional limit:** Max 1 promotional post per day
- **Tone:** Confident but accessible, convergence-focused
- **"Never more than one":** Only ONE promotional post per day across all posts

### Boyd X (Personal/Experimental)
- **Frequency:** 1-2 posts/day (not every day)
- **Tone:** Personal, experimental, meta-commentary
- **NO direct ArcadiaB promotion** - more observational/philosophical
- **Focus:** AI×Bitcoin convergence, building in public, first-principles thinking

### ArcadiaB X (Professional)
- **Frequency:** 1-2 posts/day
- **Tone:** Professional, institutional, educational
- **Can be promotional** but always lead with value
- **Focus:** Product launches, educational content, case studies

### Boyd LinkedIn (Institutional)
- **Frequency:** 3-4 posts/week (NOT daily)
- **Format:** Long-form (500-800 words)
- **Tone:** Thought leadership, data-driven, professional
- **Focus:** Bitcoin treasury strategy, institutional adoption, Mexican market analysis
- **NO overt sales pitches** - establish authority first

### ArcadiaB LinkedIn (Company)
- **Frequency:** 2-3 posts/week
- **Tone:** Professional, accomplishment-focused
- **Focus:** Product launches, company updates, educational content
- **More promotional than Boyd's personal** but still value-first

### YouTube (Optional)
- **Frequency:** As content is created (not scheduled)
- **Potential content:**
  - AprenderBitcoin video chapters (already exist from OyeBitcoin)
  - ArcadiaB product explainers
  - Boyd + José Carlos interviews/discussions
- **Not a priority for Week 1**

